  <name>ZD PLAYER</name>
  <summary>IPTV Player - Xtream &amp; M3U</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ZD PLAYER is an IPTV player application for Linux. It supports Xtream API
      and M3U playlist formats. It does not host or provide any content.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Xtream API and M3U playlist support</li>
      <li>Live TV, Movies and Series playback</li>
      <li>Multi-language interface (8 languages)</li>
      <li>Color balance, deinterlace and buffer settings</li>
      <li>Audio track and subtitle selection</li>
      <li>Fullscreen mode with overlay controls</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.zdplayer.desktop</launchable>
